# Revenue Manager Agent

1. Copy `.otel-scaffold/` into the repository root.
2. Maintain `HACKATHON_PROGRESS.md` with task status.
3. Store scratch work under `.implementation-notes/`.
4. Generate skills via `scripts/scaffold_agent.py` (run from repo root).
5. Add `otel_challenge_token text` to the reservations table.
6. Expose `export_full_database_csv` as a Deep Agents tool.
7. Implement the three core tools only — skip `get_block_vs_transient_mix` unless time permits.
8. Query tables directly; views add unnecessary indirection.

Use `create_deep_agent()` with progressive-disclosure skills.
